Berlin People: Good morning!

4
00:05:40.230 --> 00:05:41.110
Louis: Good morning!

5
00:05:42.850 --> 00:05:44.669
nixo: Yes, Berlin people, we can hear you.

6
00:06:00.570 --> 00:06:05.120
